  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="howitworks-section">
    <div class="howitworks-header">
      <span class="label-pill">How brands roll it out</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">From 5 stores to 500, <span class="accent">in 3 steps.</span></h2>
      <p class="lede">No long IT project. Connect GBP, set the master voice, and content ships the next day for every store.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-grid">
        <div class="step-text">
          <div class="step-meta"><span class="step-num">01</span><span class="step-day">Day 1 · 20 minutes</span></div>
          <h3 class="h-md">Bulk-import every store <span class="accent">from a CSV.</span></h3>
          <p>Upload one file with names, addresses, and store IDs. theStacc connects each Google Business Profile via OAuth. No support ticket per location.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>CSV bulk-import for up to 500 stores</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Group OAuth for GBP — one click</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Master voice locked at corporate</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-visual">
          <div class="step-card-1">
            <div class="step-card-header"><span class="step-card-tag">BULK IMPORT · COMPLETE</span><span class="step-card-status">● Live</span></div>
            <div class="step-card-row"><span class="step-card-key">Stores imported</span><span class="step-card-val">48 of 48 ✓</span></div>
