          <div class="step-meta"><span class="step-num">02</span><span class="step-day">Every day · Auto-pilot</span></div>
          <h3 class="h-md">Content ships <span class="accent">per store, per city.</span></h3>
          <p>While the team sleeps, theStacc writes a city-local article, posts to every GBP, and replies to every review. The brand voice holds across all 48 locations.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Daily GBP post for every store</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>1 city-local article per store, weekly</li>
