        <div class="step-text">
          <div class="step-meta"><span class="step-num">03</span><span class="step-day">1st of every month</span></div>
          <h3 class="h-md">One rollup report <span class="accent">for every region.</span></h3>
          <p>Corporate gets one chain-wide PDF. Each regional VP gets a region-level rollup. Every store manager gets a single-store report. Same data, three lenses.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Chain · region · store reports</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Rank, traffic, calls, foot-traffic estimates</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Auto-sent in your branded PDF</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-visual">
          <div class="step-card-3">
            <div class="step-card-header"><span class="step-card-tag">MONTHLY REPORT · CHAIN</span><span class="step-card-status">● Sent</span></div>
            <div class="step-stat-big">
              <span class="step-stat-num">+38%</span>
              <span class="step-stat-label">Map Pack queries · 90 days</span>
              <span class="step-stat-delta">↑ vs prior quarter</span>
